{"tid":1776240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民做搞手 間接將港豬d錢放入黃色經濟圈","createTime":"2019-12-09T11:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T17:41:09.000Z","uid":97120,"like":117,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0a41dc8966938e4aa2d86736e32a9d988eb85e","tid":1776240,"uid":97120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"港豬特色 又懶又嫌麻煩<br />\n有得食有得玩就得 所以元氣呢d仆街深藍店先仲有人幫襯<br />\n<br />\n趁聖誕節 大家身邊都會有公司藍豬 朋友港豬 話要搞party 買野食<br />\n雖然無心情但既然避唔到 點解唔將呢d錢幫襯黃店？<br />\n要幫港豬藍豬d錢消費係同路人身上<br />\n首先要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自 己 做 搞 手</span></span><br />\n主動book到會 book party house<br />\n有咁黃揀咁黃 令到d黃店有咁爆得咁爆<br />\n黃色經濟圈咁又注左一大筆資金落去 又唔洗幫襯到藍店<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVQifqY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVQifqY.png&h=dc9492a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已經有人整左黃店到會list 跟住book就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/goodwest_standwithhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgoodwest_standwithhk&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2Fz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=48e8321b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/goodwest_standwithhk</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少消費既力量 要黃色體系壯大<br />\n手足先可以得到更加多既支援<br />\n被捕手足都要有工返去維持生活<br />\n你每日洗錢習慣都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae1f9bd9c0b9d73ee582f587a668a5be94b2546","tid":1776240,"uid":97120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"自推 比錢港豬做搞手即係多個機會食美心呀！！！"},{"pid":"03c1311014bd9f690b04804eae33734851405d6a","tid":1776240,"uid":97120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"唔想食美心就自己做搞手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食美心既機會 係零呀！"},{"pid":"b2d7a71a7d937620ced8b937657c8280c733c311","tid":1776240,"uid":97120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188a19e42c2e8c321553172b3a0de238bb1e39f8","tid":1776240,"uid":97120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:56:05.000Z","msg":"美心 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580359c004964624d7040e2c9d7735d79675e892","tid":1776240,"uid":97120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"我推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61dfb1456a48cc94bf1fbfa1ab0181690eb5b591","tid":1776240,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:28:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95379b31479c7098ef3f4893168f7d3c74f6b2ec","tid":1776240,"uid":97120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔罷工 仲唔用公司錢～～"},{"pid":"c43e34478bcac1370beccf69634aadc78c7ca816","tid":1776240,"uid":94878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:47:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"554ee324cc71703a56c2669a2f2e058fdeda7f12","tid":1776240,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1554d47a8eb6d1aa16748f85a9d0113d7c969f99","tid":1776240,"uid":123456,"like":0,"disli